        Initiate verificationDialog for Mnemonics, Gmail, MobileOTP and GAuth
        Parameters:
        challengeType - Challenge type for different
        challengeType - == 1.0 == RELEASE_COIN
        challengeType - == 2.0 == CHANGE_PASSWORD
        challengeType - == 3.0 == CHANGE_EMAIL
        challengeType - == 4.0 == FORGOT_PASSWORD
        challengeType - == 5.0 == WITHDRAWAL
        ComplexityName - 2FA Verification Complexity_type
        ComplexityName - == 1 == MNEMONICS
        ComplexityName - == 2 == GOOGLE_AUTH
        ComplexityName - == 3 == MOBILE_OTP
        ComplexityName - == 4 == EMAIL_OTP
        createComplexityData - createComplexityData if Only for Mnemonics
        tradeId - tradeId is for Releasing coin and confirm payment

        walletAddress -
        amt -
